input: Ń sọ ní pàtó oye ìdádúró ọ̀kẹ́-ìṣísẹ̀ lẹ́yìn tí atọ́ka náà ti wọ agbègbè náà kí pánẹ́ẹ̀lì tó dá farahàn.Ìgbà tí bọ́tìnì ìpamọ́aládàáṣe bá jẹ́ òótọ́ nìkan ni bọ́tìnì yìí wúlò.

input: Àwọn ààtò àti àwọn ìkúndùn aládàáni

Tó bá jẹ́ òótọ́,Àwọn Ìṣàmúlò-ètò Mímọ̀ tía tòjọ nínú onísọ̀rọ̀gbèsì Rọ́ọ̀nù Ìsàmúlò-ètòwà nílẹ̀.Bóyá a fẹ ìṣàtòjọ náà tàbí a kò fẹ̀ẹ́,nígbà tí onísọ̀rọ̀gbèsì náà bá ti farahàn bọ́tìnì àtòjọàtòjọ-ètòìfihàn ló ń darí rẹ̀.
target: If true,the Known Applications listing in the Run Application dialog is made available.Whether or not the listing is expanded when the dialog is shown is controlled by the showprogramlist key.
